This module provides puppet resources to manage entities related to the DMLITE
stack of plugins and services.

It includes the classes and definitions required to install and configure
the core of DMLITE as well as all its plugins - adapter, profiler, MySQL,
memcache, etc.

More information:
https://svnweb.cern.ch/trac/lcgdm/wiki/Dpm/Dev/Dmlite
